        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1Samuel 4:11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". This foreshadowing of terrible calamity which was to befal Israel was to be a sign to Eli that all the awful predictions concerning the fate of his doomed house would be carried out to the bitter end.",
