        "text": "32. thou shalt see an enemy in my habitation—A successful rival for the office of high priest shall rise out of another family (2Sa 15:35; 1Ch 24:3; 29:22). But the marginal reading, \"thou shalt see the affliction of the tabernacle,\" seems to be a preferable translation.   ",
