        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "that shall come upon thy two sons, Hophni and Phinehas; which Eli would live to see fulfilled on them; and when it was, he might be assured the rest would be most certainly accomplished, and it was this: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "in one day they shall die both of them; as they did in battle with the Philistines, 1 Samuel 4:11. ",
